race.comment: GRIFFINSTOWN GIRL (8) ran below expectations last time after being in the firing line on the bend at Armidale, finishing ninth. Well placed and is sure to give this a mighty shake. THUNDER SHANGHAI (10) settled well back last start and failed to get into the contest when twelfth over this journey at Gatton. Looks well placed from the good draw. KNOWITALL FRANK (1) returned from a spell last start with a strong win over 1300m at Toowoomba. Fitter now and is expected to run well again. ST ROY (13) missed the placings two runs back then didn't do any better last start when fifth over 1400m at Tamworth. Finds a nice race and can make amends.
